Hypotheses Tested

Hypothesis #1



We suspected that top players are in between the ages 25 - 33.

Hypothesis #2



We think that a majority of the best players are from European countries.

Hypothesis #3



We believe strikers are not good at playing defense.

Hypothesis #4



We think that striking ability is not directly related to freekick ability. 

## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.



This plot shows a lack of any direct relationship between the two abilities.

Hypothesis #5



Attacking players are paid more than defensive players.
